{
  "title": "4.Bir Dua Öğreniyorum: İftar Duası",
  "htmlContent": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"tr\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Bir Dua Öğreniyorum: İftar Duası</title>\n    <!-- Tailwind CSS CDN -->\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com\"></script>\n    <!-- Google Fonts: Inter -->\n    <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n            background-color: #f3f4f6; /* Tailwind gray-100 */\n        }\n        \n        /* Duanın Arapça metni için özel bir font stili (daha okunaklı olması için) */\n        .dua-arabic {\n            font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; /* Cihazda bulunan geleneksel bir font */\n            font-size: 2.75rem; /* 44px */\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            text-align: right;\n            direction: rtl; /* Sağdan sola yazım yönü */\n            color: #fefce8; /* Neredeyse beyaz, yumuşak bir renk */\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"p-4 md:p-10\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto\">\n\n        <!-- Ana Başlık -->\n        <h1 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-center text-purple-800\">\n            Bir Dua Öğreniyorum\n        </h1>\n        <h2 class=\"text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-center text-purple-600 mb-10 opacity-90\" style=\"letter-spacing: -2px;\">\n            İFTAR DUASI\n        </h2>\n\n        <!-- KART 1: İftar Vaktinin Önemi -->\n        <div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 md:p-8 mb-8 overflow-hidden\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-blue-700 mb-4\">İftar Vakti ve Dua</h3>\n            <div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center\">\n                <!-- İkon -->\n                <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 mb-4 md:mb-0 md:mr-6\">\n                    <div class=\"w-20 h-20 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center\">\n                        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"currentColor\" class=\"w-10 h-10\">\n                            <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M15.182 15.182a4.5 4.5 0 01-6.364 0M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zM9.75 9.75c0 .414-.168.75-.375.75S9 10.164 9 9.75 9.168 9 9.375 9s.375.336.375.75zm.75 4.5c0 .414-.168.75-.375.75S9.75 14.664 9.75 14.25s.168-.75.375-.75.375.336.375.75zm4.5-4.5c0 .414-.168.75-.375.75s-.375-.336-.375-.75.168-.75.375-.75.375.336.375.75zm.75 4.5c0 .414-.168.75-.375.75s-.375-.336-.375-.75.168-.75.375-.75.375.336.375.75z\" />\n                        </svg>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <!-- Metin -->\n                <ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 md:pl-0 space-y-2 text-gray-700 text-lg\">\n                    <li>Oruç açılırken dua edilmesi <strong>sünnettir</strong>.</li>\n                    <li>Hz. Peygamber (sav) müjdelemiştir: <strong>\"Oruçlunun iftar vaktinde yaptığı dua geri çevrilmez.\"</strong></li>\n                    <li>Bu dua, Allah'a (cc) olan inancı, güveni ve bağlılığı dile getirir.</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- KART 2: İftar Duası (Ana Kart) -->\n        <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-700 to-blue-600 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-6 md:p-10 mb-8 text-white\">\n            \n            <!-- Arapça Metin -->\n            <div class=\"mb-6\">\n                <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-purple-200 mb-2\">Duanın Okunuşu (Arapça)</h3>\n                <p class=\"dua-arabic\">\n                    ِأَللَّ هُمَّ  لَكَ صُمُْ ت وَبِكَ آمَنُْ ت وَعَلَيَْ ك تـَوَكَّ ْلُ ت وَعَلَى رِزْقِكَ أَفْطَرُْ ت\n                </p>\n            </div>\n\n            <hr class=\"border-purple-400 opacity-50 my-8\">\n\n            <!-- Okunuşu (Transliterasyon) -->\n            <div class=\"mb-6\">\n                <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-purple-200 mb-2\">Okunuşu (Latin Harfleriyle)</h3>\n                <p class=\"text-2xl font-medium italic text-purple-100\">\n                    \"Allâhümme leke sumtü ve bike âmentü ve aleyke tevekkeltü ve alâ rızkıke eftartü.\"\n                </p>\n            </div>\n            \n            <!-- Anlamı -->\n            <div>\n                <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-purple-200 mb-2\">Anlamı</h3>\n                <p class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-white\">\n                    \"Allah’ım! Senin rızan için oruç tuttum, sana inandım, sana güvendim. Senin rızkınla orucumu açtım.\"\n                </p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <!-- KART 3: Duanın Kazandırdıkları -->\n        <div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 md:p-8\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-5\">Duanın Anlamı ve Önemi</h3>\n            <ul class=\"space-y-4\">\n                <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                    <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 mt-1\">\n                        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" class=\"w-5 h-5\">\n                            <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5\" />\n                        </svg>\n                    </div>\n                    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-800\">Allah'a (cc) olan <strong>inancımızı</strong> ve teslimiyetimizi ifade ederiz.</span>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                    <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 mt-1\">\n                        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" class=\"w-5 h-5\">\n                            <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5\" />\n                        </svg>\n                    </div>\n                    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-800\">Yalnızca O'na <strong>güvendiğimizi</strong> (tevekkül ettiğimizi) belirtiriz.</span>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                    <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 mt-1\">\n                        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" class=\"w-5 h-5\">\n                            <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5\" />\n                        </svg>\n                    </div>\n                    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-800\">Verdiği bütün nimetler için O'na <strong>şükretmiş</strong> oluruz.</span>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                    <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 mt-1\">\n                        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" class=\"w-5 h-5\">\n                            <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5\" />\n                        </svg>\n                    </div>\n                    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-800\">Oruç tutan kişinin <strong>ibadet bilincini</strong> güçlendirir.</span>\n                </li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
}